snippet.title: Amber Heard Flaunts Her Midriff in a Slashed White Ensemble at Star-Studded Luncheon - Splash News
snippet.description:
Amber Heard wows as she joins Nicole Kidman, Eva Longoria and Liam Hemsworth at the 2013 Hollywood Foreign Press Association's Luncheon.

Splash brings the hottest, most up-to-date Hollywood stories and photos to millions of people round the world through their favourite newspapers, magazines and TV station. We don't deal in gossip.
